      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"2. GAMBINO showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing sixth (23.17) in a Mix 3/4 at Gosford. Solid record at the distance winning 10 races. Has ability and looks hard to stop. 3. FUMBLES has been in super consistent form recently with three minors on end before missing the frame latest finishing fourth (17.86) at this track. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to his name from five starts. Cannot be left out. 1. WEEONA STAR first look at this trip and drops in distance on last start. Should get a good run from the inside box. With even luck and a clean start should be around the money. 8. STRAIGHT OUT can feature with the right run.\",\"runners\":[2,3,1,8],\"exclusive\":false}",
